# API Endpoints Reference

This document lists **all API endpoints** for the CHQI-RAG backend, hosted at: https://chqi-rag.onrender.com

---

## Authentication

### POST `/api/auth/login`
- **Body:** `{ email, password }` or `{ username, password }`
- **Description:** Login for all user types. Returns JWT token and user info.

### GET `/api/auth/me`
- **Headers:** `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
- **Description:** Get current user profile (requires authentication).

---

## Chatbot

### GET `/api/chatbot/session/:clientid`
- **Params:** `clientid` (patient UUID)
- **Description:** Fetch patient session info by patient id.

### POST `/api/chatbot/login`
- **Body:** `{ phone, ccc_number }`
- **Description:** Login for client chat (returns patient session info).

### POST `/api/chatbot/message`
- **Body:** `{ message, patient_id }`
- **Description:** Send a message as a patient (client chat).

### GET `/api/chatbot/history/:patientId`
- **Params:** `patientId` (UUID)
- **Description:** Get chat history for a patient.

---

## Patients

### GET `/api/patients`
- **Query:** `facility_id`, `risk_level`, `search`, `page`, `limit`
- **Description:** List patients with filtering and pagination.

### GET `/api/patients/facilities`
- **Description:** List all facilities.

### GET `/api/patients/stats`
- **Description:** Get patient statistics.

### GET `/api/patients/:patientId`
- **Params:** `patientId` (UUID)
- **Description:** Get patient details.

### GET `/api/patients/search/ccc/:cccNumber`
- **Params:** `cccNumber`
- **Description:** Search for a patient by CCC number.

### GET `/api/patients/facility/:facilityId/list`
- **Params:** `facilityId`
- **Description:** List patients in a specific facility.

### POST `/api/patients/facility/:facilityId/create`
- **Body:** Patient data
- **Description:** Create new patient in facility.

### PUT `/api/patients/:patientId`
- **Body:** Patient data
- **Description:** Update patient information.

### POST `/api/patients/:patientId/ccc`
- **Body:** `{ cccNumber, enrollmentDate, facilityId }`
- **Description:** Add CCC number to patient.

### GET `/api/patients/facility/:facilityId/report`
- **Query:** `startDate`, `endDate`
- **Description:** Get patient report for date range.

---

## RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)

### POST `/api/rag/query`
- **Body:** `{ message, phone, channel }`
- **Description:** Query the RAG system (for SMS/WhatsApp/other channels).

---

## Conversations

### GET `/api/conversations`
- **Query:** `page`, `limit`, `phone`, `channel`, `startDate`, `endDate`
- **Description:** List conversations with filtering and pagination.

### GET `/api/conversations/:id`
- **Params:** `id`
- **Description:** Get a single conversation by ID.

### GET `/api/conversations/phone/:phoneNumber`
- **Params:** `phoneNumber`
- **Description:** Get conversations by phone number.

---

## Health

### GET `/api/health`
- **Description:** Health check endpoint.

---

## Other Notable Endpoints

- **Documents:** `/api/documents` (GET, POST for upload, etc.)
- **Analytics:** `/api/analytics/dashboard-stats`, `/api/analytics/daily`, etc.
- **Facilities:** `/api/facilities` (GET, POST, etc.)
- **Admin:** `/api/admin/dashboard`, `/api/admin/users-list`, etc.
- **Webhooks:** `/api/webhooks/sms/receive`, `/api/webhooks/whatsapp/receive` (POST)
- **Flagged:** `/api/flagged` (GET, POST, etc.)

---

**Notes:**
- All endpoints are prefixed with `/api/`.
- Most endpoints require authentication via JWT in the `Authorization` header.
- Use the correct HTTP method (`GET`, `POST`, etc.) as shown.
- For POST/PUT, send data as JSON in the request body.
- For GET, use query parameters or URL params as needed.

For more details on each endpoint, see the corresponding route file in `server/routes/`.
